                                                                                              NIST SP 800-70 REV. 4                                         NATIONAL CHECKLIST PROGRAM FOR IT PRODUCTS



                                                                                                      Field Name                                                Description

                                                                                                                         The IT product’s operational environment, such as Standalone, Managed, or Custom
                                                                                                Target Operational       (with description, such as Specialized Security-Limited Functionality, Legacy, or United
                                                                                                Environment              States Government). Generally only applicable for security compliance/vulnerability
                                                                                                                         checklists.
                                                                                                Checklist Type           The type of checklist, such as Compliance, Vulnerability, and Specialized.
                                                                                                Checklist Installation   Describes the functional tools required to use the checklist to configure the system, if
                                                                                                Tools                    they are not included with the checklist.
                                                                                                FIPS 140-2 Compliance    Whether the product can operate in a FIPS 140-2 validated mode (yes or no).
                                                                                                                         Whether the checklist is consistent with various regulations and standards (e.g., Health
                                                                                                                         information Portability and Accountability Act [HIPAA], Gramm-Leach-Bliley Act [GLBA],
                                                                                                                         FISMA [such as mappings to NIST SP 800-53 controls], ISO 27001, Sarbanes-Oxley,
